WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.300 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 5]

03:00.350 --> 03:01.280
What are you doing?

03:01.860 --> 03:02.590
You have the antidote.

03:02.590 --> 03:03.940
Why didn't you save us?

03:03.970 --> 03:04.770
Why?

03:16.400 --> 03:17.079
Step back!

03:17.100 --> 03:18.630
Step back! Don't push!

03:19.860 --> 03:25.270
[Bai Residence]

03:37.960 --> 03:38.910
Master,

03:38.930 --> 03:39.770
Cold Spring Palace has spread the news

03:39.800 --> 03:41.170
that the Governor's Mansion has the antidote.

03:41.200 --> 03:43.150
All the uninfected people in the city are besieging the Governor's Mansion.

03:43.170 --> 03:45.240
Bai Shuo was sent out of the city by her father.

03:45.460 --> 03:47.590
Bai Xun doesn't know that Bai Shuo is afflicted with Nether Poison.

03:47.610 --> 03:49.450
Without Ghost Grass to suppress it,

03:49.480 --> 03:50.710
won't she go mad?

04:08.530 --> 04:09.220
Uncle Wang,

04:09.250 --> 04:10.710
stop! Send me back!

04:11.950 --> 04:13.330
I said stop!

04:15.000 --> 04:16.240
Stop the carriage!

04:28.940 --> 04:29.650
Lady Shuo!

04:29.680 --> 04:30.410
Lady Shuo!

04:30.860 --> 04:32.150
You can't go!

04:32.170 --> 04:33.370
You can't go back!

04:33.610 --> 04:35.280
I know my father well.

04:35.310 --> 04:36.000
If I leave,

04:36.000 --> 04:36.950
he will die.

04:36.950 --> 04:38.600
-Let go!
-Lady Shuo!

04:39.040 --> 04:40.260
The governor's order was a military command.

04:40.510 --> 04:41.390
No matter what happens,

04:41.390 --> 04:42.390
I must take you away.

04:42.520 --> 04:43.690
Military orders must be obeyed.

04:43.940 --> 04:45.670
I must take you away!

04:47.630 --> 04:48.310
Okay.

04:48.540 --> 04:49.390
Okay.

04:50.060 --> 04:51.420
I'll go get the horse.

04:55.750 --> 04:56.790
Sorry.

05:01.010 --> 05:02.250
With this horse,

05:02.280 --> 05:03.920
you won't be able to reach Ning'an City before it's destroyed.

05:06.270 --> 05:07.040
Fan Yue?

05:08.210 --> 05:09.780
She didn't go mad?

05:10.470 --> 05:12.060
It seems the Nether Poison doesn't work on her.

05:12.630 --> 05:14.480
Is it because the Desireless Stone is in her body?

05:16.200 --> 05:17.320
If you want to return to Ning'an City,

05:18.270 --> 05:19.550
I'll take you back.

05:55.270 --> 05:56.270
You three,

05:56.290 --> 05:58.460
quickly go and restrain the people who have gone mad in the city.

05:58.640 --> 05:59.310
Yes.

06:10.040 --> 06:11.240
Master Bright Moon?

06:12.720 --> 06:13.350
Fan Yue,

06:13.380 --> 06:14.190
let her go!

06:14.560 --> 06:16.750
Are they the Eternals you've been wanting to become?

06:17.720 --> 06:19.400
The Lanling Eternals?

06:19.430 --> 06:20.660
So this is Bai Shuo?

06:21.530 --> 06:22.300
Yes.

06:26.790 --> 06:27.880
Leave now.

06:43.510 --> 06:44.340
Fan Yue,

06:44.360 --> 06:46.230
there has long been an agreement between the Eternal and Demon Races

06:46.250 --> 06:47.690
to not harm the Human Race.

06:47.720 --> 06:49.310
Yet you not only stole the Desireless Stone,

06:49.330 --> 06:50.860
but also caused chaos among the Human Race.

06:51.090 --> 06:52.210
So what?

06:53.120 --> 06:54.310
Jin Yao,

06:54.330 --> 06:56.020
the Desireless Stone and Bai Shuo are both mine.

06:56.840 --> 06:57.830
If you don't want your Lanling Sect

06:57.830 --> 06:59.270
to be wiped out in Ning'an today,

07:00.040 --> 07:01.630
get out of my sight.

07:01.840 --> 07:03.340
How arrogant!

07:08.840 --> 07:09.520
Shuo!

07:09.540 --> 07:10.560
The city is full of demons.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.000
They all want to take the Desireless Stone.

07:12.090 --> 07:13.270
It's too dangerous for you to stay here.

07:13.270 --> 07:14.120
With Master and Uncle Master here,

07:14.120 --> 07:15.150
they will surely keep Uncle Bai safe.

07:15.170 --> 07:16.320
Come back to Lanling Sect with me.

07:17.440 --> 07:18.230
Let go!

07:18.690 --> 07:19.300
Chong Zhao,

07:20.040 --> 07:20.720
I won't trust

07:20.720 --> 07:21.930
those who have lied to me.

07:22.340 --> 07:23.860
I'm going back to find my father.

07:23.880 --> 07:24.920
I don't have time to listen to your nonsense.

07:25.320 --> 07:26.120
Shuo!

07:26.150 --> 07:26.960
Let her go!

07:38.250 --> 07:39.130
Shuo!

07:50.370 --> 07:53.900
[Peaceful]

07:51.650 --> 07:52.650
Grand Master,

07:52.870 --> 07:54.010
as you expected,

07:54.040 --> 07:55.850
Bai Shuo was brought back by Fan Yue.

07:55.870 --> 07:57.110
The Five Eternals of Lanling have also arrived

07:57.140 --> 07:58.550
and are currently fighting with Fan Yue.

07:59.830 --> 08:02.710
Although the Five Eternals of Lanling can't kill Fan Yue,

08:02.730 --> 08:04.210
they can at least hold him off.

08:06.810 --> 08:08.050
See?

08:08.680 --> 08:09.560
Remember,

08:09.600 --> 08:11.140
the Nether Poison is just the prelude

08:11.170 --> 08:13.100
to the chaos in Ning'an City.

08:14.090 --> 08:14.800
Go.

08:15.140 --> 08:16.250
Bai Shuo will be here soon.

08:16.790 --> 08:17.660
Yes.

08:17.690 --> 08:19.500
I know what to do.

08:24.310 --> 08:28.060
[Bai Residence]

08:31.670 --> 08:33.860
Give us the antidote!

08:44.120 --> 08:45.760
Sheathe the swords!

08:57.420 --> 08:58.420
Governor,

08:58.450 --> 08:59.970
please give me the antidote

08:59.990 --> 09:01.590
and save my baby!

09:01.620 --> 09:02.530
Please save him.

09:02.550 --> 09:03.550
Please.

09:03.750 --> 09:05.230
Please save him!

09:05.250 --> 09:06.720
Please save him, Governor!

09:07.310 --> 09:08.690
Please!

09:09.150 --> 09:10.240
Governor.

09:13.630 --> 09:14.950
There's no antidote

09:16.110 --> 09:17.080
in the Governor's Mansion.

09:18.750 --> 09:19.950
I can't save him.

09:20.720 --> 09:21.480
You don't have the antidote?

09:21.480 --> 09:22.550
It's impossible!

09:28.090 --> 09:30.010
How can you not have the antidote?

09:30.030 --> 09:32.020
You just don't care about us!

09:32.050 --> 09:33.330
Give us the antidote!

09:33.350 --> 09:34.560
We know you have the antidote!

09:34.590 --> 09:35.590
Take it out!

09:39.280 --> 09:40.260
Bai Xun!

09:40.660 --> 09:41.430
Father!

09:41.700 --> 09:43.130
Look at me!

09:43.750 --> 09:44.390
Father!

09:45.270 --> 09:45.910
Bai Xun!

09:45.910 --> 09:46.960
Stop yelling.

09:46.990 --> 09:48.150
With the barrier here,

09:48.170 --> 09:49.410
they can't hear

09:49.440 --> 09:50.560
or see you.

09:51.190 --> 09:52.670
What exactly do you want?

09:52.690 --> 09:53.660
Let me pass!

09:54.390 --> 09:55.430
Don't be impatient.

09:55.450 --> 09:56.930
Since you've come back,

09:57.470 --> 09:58.910
how about watching a show?

10:00.730 --> 10:01.560
If you don't have the antidote,

10:01.580 --> 10:03.110
why are you still alive?

10:03.140 --> 10:03.940
Bai Xun!

10:03.960 --> 10:05.440
We've always trusted you,

10:05.460 --> 10:06.230
admired you,

10:06.260 --> 10:07.540
and regarded you as the governor!

10:07.560 --> 10:09.200
You're even unwilling to save a child!

10:09.230 --> 10:11.330
Where's your conscience?

10:17.720 --> 10:18.600
Bai Xun,

10:18.600 --> 10:19.790
you're selfish

10:19.790 --> 10:21.360
and indifferent to the people in the city!

10:21.360 --> 10:22.910
What kind of governor are you?

10:22.910 --> 10:25.030
You're even worse than a beast!

10:26.430 --> 10:28.440
You don't deserve to be the governor!

10:28.630 --> 10:30.240
You're useless!

10:30.240 --> 10:31.670
Give us the antidote!

10:31.670 --> 10:32.870
Are you even human?

10:32.870 --> 10:34.360
You find it unbelievable, right?

10:35.200 --> 10:36.720
From respect to hatred,

10:36.740 --> 10:38.100
it only took one day.

10:38.200 --> 10:40.510
How could you not care about us?

10:41.930 --> 10:43.680
Now that things have come to this,

10:43.700 --> 10:45.410
how about we make it even more exciting?

10:52.310 --> 10:53.150
Governor?

10:59.750 --> 11:00.910
Screw you!

11:16.970 --> 11:18.220
The governor has gone mad!

11:20.770 --> 11:21.540
Governor?

11:22.970 --> 11:23.790
Governor!

11:24.290 --> 11:26.290
He's gone mad! Run!

11:32.240 --> 11:33.000
Governor!

11:33.150 --> 11:34.530
Let's run!

11:34.940 --> 11:36.380
The outside is full of madmen!

11:36.400 --> 11:38.040
Only the Governor's Mansion is safe!

11:38.080 --> 11:39.830
Where else can we escape to?

11:39.850 --> 11:41.250
Bai Xun is highly skilled in martial arts.

11:41.280 --> 11:42.590
While he hasn't completely lost control,

11:42.610 --> 11:43.570
let's kill him now!

11:43.600 --> 11:45.170
Otherwise, when he completely loses his sanity,

11:45.200 --> 11:46.960
-we'll be the ones who die!
-Kill him!

11:46.960 --> 11:49.530
They are the people Bai Xun wants to protect—

11:49.560 --> 11:50.760
ungrateful,

11:50.780 --> 11:52.150
murderous.

11:52.180 --> 11:54.450
Even I, a demon, can't compare to them.

11:54.570 --> 11:55.520
Bai Shuo,

11:55.550 --> 11:56.840
why don't you stop being a human

11:56.860 --> 11:58.340
and join our Demon Race?

11:58.370 --> 11:59.960
The Desireless Stone is inside you.

11:59.980 --> 12:01.580
If you work for the Grand Master,

12:01.630 --> 12:02.630
he

12:02.650 --> 12:04.090
will surely be pleased.

12:04.120 --> 12:05.360
Shut up!

12:05.380 --> 12:07.110
Detoxify my father!

12:07.140 --> 12:08.420
As you know,

12:08.560 --> 12:09.760
there's no cure for this poison.

12:09.780 --> 12:10.930
It's either death or madness.

12:11.240 --> 12:12.710
Today,

12:12.730 --> 12:14.410
someone has to die.

12:15.110 --> 12:16.110
Kill him!

12:16.130 --> 12:17.530
Kill him!

12:17.560 --> 12:18.270
Die!

12:25.350 --> 12:26.510
Kill him!

12:27.400 --> 12:28.610
Stop!

12:29.200 --> 12:30.420
Stop beating him!

12:30.880 --> 12:31.720
Beat him!

12:31.740 --> 12:32.760
Beat him!

12:36.000 --> 12:37.840
Father, wake up!

12:37.870 --> 12:38.880
Beat him!

12:39.320 --> 12:39.720
Beat him!

12:39.720 --> 12:41.080
What are you doing?

12:41.080 --> 12:42.120
Governor!

12:43.660 --> 12:45.000
Stop it!

12:45.030 --> 12:46.260
Father!

13:00.150 --> 13:01.150
No!

13:01.150 --> 13:02.650
Don't bite my father!

13:02.870 --> 13:04.720
Father, wake up! Father!

13:06.280 --> 13:07.960
Let go of my father!

13:08.000 --> 13:09.200
Let go of my father!

13:09.200 --> 13:11.050
Don't bite my father!

13:15.110 --> 13:16.590
Let go of my father!

13:16.620 --> 13:18.140
Let go of my father!

13:18.160 --> 13:19.020
Go.

13:19.610 --> 13:20.570
Go!

13:29.080 --> 13:31.450
Father, wake up! Father!

13:41.420 --> 13:42.750
Father!

13:45.750 --> 13:46.550
Governor!

13:52.530 --> 13:54.400
I'll kill you!

13:54.470 --> 13:56.680
I swear I'll kill you!

14:00.530 --> 14:02.900
I'm incompetent!

14:03.160 --> 14:05.260
I can't save you.

14:05.940 --> 14:07.390
This maniac condition...

14:08.210 --> 14:10.690
really has no cure!

14:13.120 --> 14:14.280
Bai Yu!

14:14.930 --> 14:15.970
Hurry!

14:16.000 --> 14:18.600
Take the people out of Ning'an City!

14:18.620 --> 14:19.670
Hurry!

14:21.860 --> 14:22.720
Father!

14:32.110 --> 14:33.320
I don't know...

14:35.630 --> 14:39.290
why Ning'an is suffering this calamity,

14:40.890 --> 14:42.210
but I know...

14:41.320 --> 14:44.560
♫Across thousands of miles♫

14:43.170 --> 14:45.630
that there are gods in this world!

14:46.120 --> 14:48.560
Gods!

14:49.270 --> 14:50.320
I, Bai Xun,

14:49.440 --> 14:54.250
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

14:50.840 --> 14:53.510
am willing to offer my life

14:55.250 --> 14:57.290
to seek your mercy!

14:56.740 --> 15:04.020
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

14:58.020 --> 15:00.290
Please descend upon Ning'an

15:00.390 --> 15:01.550
and save

15:01.550 --> 15:03.960
the people of Ning'an!

15:05.140 --> 15:10.180
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

15:07.230 --> 15:08.270
I am willing

15:08.290 --> 15:10.130
to exchange my life

15:11.320 --> 15:12.750
for the peace...

15:12.750 --> 15:14.030
Governor! Governor!

15:14.030 --> 15:15.330
No!

15:16.200 --> 15:17.200
Governor!

15:17.200 --> 15:18.600
Of a city!

15:21.120 --> 15:22.510
Father!

15:22.130 --> 15:24.030
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

15:23.600 --> 15:24.840
Governor!

15:24.360 --> 15:26.330
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

15:26.390 --> 15:28.180
♫My love brought tears♫

15:28.430 --> 15:30.150
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

15:30.570 --> 15:32.400
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

15:32.610 --> 15:34.030
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

15:34.240 --> 15:35.860
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

15:36.230 --> 15:38.210
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

15:38.570 --> 15:40.150
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

15:40.400 --> 15:42.050
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

15:42.320 --> 15:44.430
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

15:44.740 --> 15:46.320
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

15:46.640 --> 15:48.430
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

15:48.700 --> 15:50.710
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

15:51.000 --> 15:52.500
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

15:52.700 --> 15:55.160
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

16:00.130 --> 16:04.100
♫The flowers flew away♫

16:07.600 --> 16:11.710
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

16:15.560 --> 16:16.800
Don't sleep.

16:15.710 --> 16:22.860
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

16:17.050 --> 16:18.480
You can't sleep!

16:19.040 --> 16:20.610
I don't allow you to die!

16:22.330 --> 16:23.670
Didn't you say you would wait with me

16:23.310 --> 16:29.460
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

16:23.670 --> 16:26.080
for Xi to come back?

16:26.080 --> 16:28.510
Xi hasn't come back yet.

16:28.510 --> 16:30.150
You can't die!

16:33.720 --> 16:35.240
It's all your fault!

16:35.680 --> 16:37.270
It's because of you!

16:37.300 --> 16:39.210
I'll kill you!

16:46.600 --> 16:47.510
Father,

16:47.530 --> 16:48.900
I can save you.

16:48.930 --> 16:50.540
I'll find someone to save you.

16:50.790 --> 16:51.630
Hang in there.

16:51.630 --> 16:53.510
I will find someone to save you.

16:51.710 --> 16:54.010
[Bai Residence]

16:54.580 --> 16:55.800
Hang in there.

17:25.810 --> 17:29.840
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

17:30.080 --> 17:31.800
♫My love brought tears♫

17:31.980 --> 17:33.870
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

17:34.000 --> 17:35.910
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

17:36.210 --> 17:37.670
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

17:37.850 --> 17:39.480
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

17:40.000 --> 17:41.670
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

17:41.960 --> 17:43.690
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

17:43.960 --> 17:45.700
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

17:46.080 --> 17:47.940
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

17:48.120 --> 17:50.080
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

17:50.240 --> 17:51.960
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

17:52.330 --> 17:54.290
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

17:54.500 --> 17:56.040
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

17:56.330 --> 17:58.680
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

18:44.080 --> 18:45.390
One of the Five Contemplations

18:45.410 --> 18:46.580
was awakened?

18:46.610 --> 18:47.520
It's golden.

18:47.840 --> 18:48.990
Kindness?

18:49.010 --> 18:50.580
The first Contemplation is not killing,

18:50.950 --> 18:51.870
but kindness!

19:33.910 --> 19:34.570
Bai Shuo.

19:35.030 --> 19:35.650
Bai Shuo.

19:56.160 --> 19:56.960
Let's go.

20:14.420 --> 20:15.450
Did you see that?

20:15.890 --> 20:16.920
Are they immortals?

20:16.920 --> 20:18.100
My baby is cured!

20:18.120 --> 20:18.830
My baby is cured!

20:18.830 --> 20:19.480
Sect Leader.

20:19.830 --> 20:21.400
He's really cured!

20:21.570 --> 20:23.370
They are really immortals!

20:23.400 --> 20:25.040
They are really immortals!

20:39.820 --> 20:42.140
-Are you okay? Let me see.
-I'm fine.

20:42.170 --> 20:43.220
Great!

20:45.200 --> 20:47.190
Great!

20:50.310 --> 20:51.680
We're fine now.

20:52.610 --> 20:54.560
I didn't expect to see you again.

20:58.030 --> 21:01.420
Thank you, immortals! Thank you, immortals!

21:01.440 --> 21:06.050
Thank you, immortals! Thank you, immortals!

21:16.420 --> 21:17.310
Put her down!

21:19.290 --> 21:21.000
The Human Race has suffered heavy losses.

21:21.020 --> 21:22.940
How about we call a truce between the Eternals and demons today?

21:22.970 --> 21:24.760
Bai Xun just died.

21:25.070 --> 21:27.200
Aren't you going to let them

21:27.200 --> 21:28.440
say their final goodbyes?

21:39.480 --> 21:41.880
The Lanling Sect always stands by its word.

21:41.880 --> 21:42.880
Are you afraid

21:42.880 --> 21:45.310
that we'll take her in front of you?

21:46.730 --> 21:47.400
Master,

21:47.420 --> 21:48.350
don't believe him.

21:48.380 --> 21:49.300
You're injured.

21:49.320 --> 21:51.090
We should take Bai Shuo back to the Polar Realm as soon as possible.

22:25.680 --> 22:27.740
The road ahead is not yours to take.

22:35.400 --> 22:36.070
Sir?

22:40.000 --> 22:41.160
Is this the Lunar Hidden Sea?

22:41.550 --> 22:42.110
Yes.

22:43.350 --> 22:44.240
And no.

22:44.880 --> 22:46.490
This is your sea of consciousness.

22:46.510 --> 22:47.550
What you see

22:47.580 --> 22:48.930
is just my consciousness.

22:49.620 --> 22:50.580
Bai Shuo,

22:50.610 --> 22:51.700
your father's death

22:52.200 --> 22:53.330
caused you great pain.

22:56.440 --> 22:57.240
Sir,

22:57.260 --> 22:59.020
I'm begging you, please save my father.

22:59.200 --> 23:01.130
You saved me ten years ago,

23:01.160 --> 23:02.200
which was already a great kindness.

23:02.790 --> 23:04.730
I know I have no right to ask for more,

23:06.150 --> 23:08.190
but my father loved the city and protected the people

23:08.210 --> 23:09.650
with loyalty throughout his life.

23:09.720 --> 23:10.790
Until the moment of his death,

23:10.790 --> 23:12.540
he never gave up on being kind.

23:13.000 --> 23:14.980
He is the one who truly deserves to live.

23:15.710 --> 23:17.280
Please, I beg you to save him.

23:18.310 --> 23:19.000
Or...

23:19.720 --> 23:21.510
or give my life to him

23:21.510 --> 23:22.440
and let him live.

23:23.310 --> 23:24.200
You want to die?

23:25.160 --> 23:26.200
I don't want to die.

23:28.160 --> 23:29.670
But I have no other choices now.

23:30.230 --> 23:31.940
Only gods can bring someone

23:32.480 --> 23:33.590
back to life.

23:34.360 --> 23:34.960
No.

23:35.540 --> 23:36.680
You're wrong.

23:37.480 --> 23:39.450
The one who can interfere with life and death isn't me—

23:41.140 --> 23:41.940
it's you.

23:42.790 --> 23:43.400
Me?

23:45.220 --> 23:46.700
Eternals can't save him,

23:46.730 --> 23:47.910
and demons can't save him.

23:48.790 --> 23:49.960
I'm just a mortal.

23:50.000 --> 23:51.160
How can I save him?

23:51.160 --> 23:52.880
As long as you have enough power,

23:53.560 --> 23:54.520
you can.

23:55.240 --> 23:56.720
Enough power?

23:59.710 --> 24:01.900
How can I have enough power?

24:02.330 --> 24:03.770
Gather the contemplations

24:03.790 --> 24:05.410
and reignite the Desireless Stone.

24:06.020 --> 24:07.590
Reignite the Desireless Stone?

24:08.400 --> 24:09.530
Bai Shuo,

24:09.550 --> 24:10.580
remember,

24:10.610 --> 24:12.200
the meaning of your existence

24:12.400 --> 24:14.210
isn't to repay someone's kindness,

24:14.640 --> 24:16.360
nor to live for anyone else.

24:17.090 --> 24:18.650
The Desireless Stone entering your body

24:18.870 --> 24:19.930
is both a serendipity

24:20.090 --> 24:21.200
and a part of the cycle of cause and effect.

24:21.610 --> 24:23.050
When the heavens bestow great responsibilities,

24:23.080 --> 24:24.290
they come with trials.

24:24.820 --> 24:26.110
There's no way ahead.

24:26.470 --> 24:27.830
No destruction, no construction.

24:28.080 --> 24:29.230
You

24:29.520 --> 24:31.200
must carve your own path.

24:32.420 --> 24:34.280
What is my own path?

24:38.940 --> 24:39.700
Sir,

24:39.730 --> 24:41.250
who are you?

24:41.270 --> 24:42.530
One day,

24:42.590 --> 24:43.980
you will know.

24:53.160 --> 24:53.960
Father.

24:57.360 --> 24:58.190
Where is my father?

24:59.640 --> 25:00.480
Where is my father?

25:09.020 --> 25:12.630
[Noble Virtue]

25:13.170 --> 25:17.710
[Memorial Tablet of My Late Father, Bai Xun]

25:38.780 --> 25:41.640
♫I remember that moonlit night♫

25:42.480 --> 25:45.020
♫The flowers that bloomed once in a lifetime♫

25:45.840 --> 25:49.600
♫I remember that word of concern♫

25:50.230 --> 25:53.470
♫But unfortunately, I didn't get to answer♫

25:53.970 --> 25:56.620
♫I remember that drop of tear♫

25:57.540 --> 26:00.930
♫It dried in the wind♫

26:01.610 --> 26:03.260
♫The one in the autumn wind♫

26:03.790 --> 26:07.400
♫How many times have I seen you in my dreams?♫

26:08.440 --> 26:11.640
♫That year, that year♫

26:12.220 --> 26:15.430
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

26:16.050 --> 26:19.560
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

26:20.190 --> 26:22.680
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

26:23.640 --> 26:26.960
♫That year, that year♫

26:27.400 --> 26:30.580
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

26:31.390 --> 26:34.520
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

26:35.670 --> 26:38.400
♫Layer after layer♫

26:39.120 --> 26:41.600
♫Another year passed♫

26:49.050 --> 26:52.180
♫That year, that year♫

26:52.860 --> 26:56.070
♫The leaves fell unnoticed after the flowers bloomed♫

26:56.660 --> 26:59.920
♫I'm afraid the autumn wind will stir up memories♫

27:00.920 --> 27:03.680
♫They unfold, one page after another♫

27:04.560 --> 27:07.920
♫That year, that year♫

27:08.240 --> 27:11.510
♫The flowers flew under the moon, filling the sky♫

27:12.310 --> 27:15.490
♫Falling to the mud, burying the memories♫

27:16.540 --> 27:19.120
♫Layer after layer♫

27:20.230 --> 27:23.670
♫Another year passed♫

27:33.200 --> 27:33.960
Mom.

27:33.960 --> 27:35.920
Ning'an City is in this state

27:35.940 --> 27:38.170
because of the Eternal Race's negligence.

27:38.370 --> 27:40.760
But isn't the Bright Moon Palace also responsible for this?

27:41.490 --> 27:43.490
You're injured now.

27:43.520 --> 27:45.650
And we're not afraid of war.

27:45.680 --> 27:48.050
If the 72 sects of the Eternals unite,

27:48.070 --> 27:50.420
the Bright Moon Palace would have no chance to win.

27:50.450 --> 27:51.950
Do you think

27:52.530 --> 27:54.290
you can use this threat on me?

27:54.630 --> 27:56.140
It's not a threat.

27:56.370 --> 27:58.500
If it really comes to a war,

27:58.520 --> 28:00.760
it's still the common people who will suffer.

28:00.790 --> 28:03.080
This is not what we want.

28:03.780 --> 28:05.960
You must have taken Bai Shuo in

28:06.030 --> 28:08.590
out of compassion, right?

28:10.310 --> 28:11.570
Compassion?

28:13.250 --> 28:14.340
Ridiculous.

28:14.370 --> 28:15.440
Whether it's out of compassion or not,

28:15.440 --> 28:18.080
only you know.

28:18.110 --> 28:19.390
Whether she joins the Eternals

28:19.410 --> 28:20.680
or the demons,

28:20.990 --> 28:23.120
let Bai Shuo decide for herself.

28:51.990 --> 28:52.630
Does it hurt?

28:59.430 --> 29:00.050
Wipe it off.

29:02.100 --> 29:03.270
Thank you, Grand Master.

29:04.250 --> 29:05.290
Do you know

29:05.320 --> 29:06.480
why I punished you?

29:07.290 --> 29:09.330
Because I saved Chong Zhao,

29:10.360 --> 29:12.040
which led to the failure of framing the blame.

29:12.330 --> 29:13.440
Lanling Sect is now targeting

29:13.470 --> 29:14.640
the Cold Spring Palace.

29:15.590 --> 29:16.180
Wrong.

29:16.490 --> 29:18.050
When you first intervened to save him,

29:18.380 --> 29:19.420
I told you

29:19.450 --> 29:21.410
I wouldn't punish you, so I didn't.

29:21.890 --> 29:23.570
What angered me is that

29:23.940 --> 29:26.600
you made the same mistake for the second time.

29:30.580 --> 29:32.580
Do you think I couldn't see through it?

29:32.640 --> 29:33.570
In front of

29:33.590 --> 29:34.870
the Governor's Mansion,

29:34.900 --> 29:36.290
you took the initiative to step in

29:36.310 --> 29:37.710
and lend a hand,

29:38.000 --> 29:39.890
and it was still to save Chong Zhao.

29:40.520 --> 29:42.390
It seems our Lady Fu Ling

29:42.420 --> 29:44.140
has someone special on her mind now.

29:44.160 --> 29:45.230
Unfortunately,

29:45.270 --> 29:46.680
he is an Eternal.

29:46.710 --> 29:47.950
I can accept any punishment

29:47.970 --> 29:49.250
from Grand Master.

29:49.310 --> 29:51.040
But it's not your place to sow discord between us.

29:51.070 --> 29:51.920
That's right.

29:55.990 --> 29:57.360
But I'm also curious,

29:57.380 --> 29:58.410
what exactly

29:58.440 --> 29:59.760
are your feelings

29:59.780 --> 30:00.980
for that Chong Zhao now?

30:05.630 --> 30:07.110
I have no particular feelings for him.

30:07.130 --> 30:09.090
As I said before,

30:09.200 --> 30:10.680
besides repaying his kindness,

30:10.700 --> 30:12.460
I also want him to join our Cold Spring Palace

30:12.490 --> 30:13.820
and work for you.

30:14.850 --> 30:15.880
Great.

30:17.520 --> 30:18.590
Well then,

30:18.610 --> 30:19.820
let's do as you said

30:20.900 --> 30:22.090
and turn him into a demon.

30:22.280 --> 30:22.870
How about this?

30:23.520 --> 30:24.280
I...

30:24.860 --> 30:26.170
will give you some more time.

30:26.480 --> 30:27.480
One month.

30:27.510 --> 30:28.350
How about one month?

30:28.940 --> 30:29.870
Within one month,

30:29.960 --> 30:31.750
make him work for our Cold Spring Palace.

30:32.640 --> 30:33.760
If you fail,

30:34.350 --> 30:35.350
then

30:35.640 --> 30:37.930
I'll have to step in

30:38.600 --> 30:39.810
and end him.

30:42.240 --> 30:43.520
Understood?

30:44.270 --> 30:45.070
Yes.

30:48.160 --> 30:48.970
Go.

31:06.590 --> 31:08.160
I allowed you to kowtow to him

31:10.340 --> 31:12.300
because he deserved it.

31:13.110 --> 31:14.270
But Chong Zhao,

31:15.900 --> 31:17.380
from now on,

31:20.000 --> 31:21.420
you're no longer a member of the Bai family.

31:25.960 --> 31:29.410
Ever since my father was chosen as the governor,

31:30.270 --> 31:32.310
he prepared this coffin.

31:33.510 --> 31:35.400
I know he was not afraid of death,

31:37.270 --> 31:38.640
but I never imagined

31:38.670 --> 31:40.700
he would leave me like this.

31:43.780 --> 31:46.830
The one who always wants to cultivate immortality is me.

31:50.750 --> 31:52.240
The one who was self-righteous

31:53.880 --> 31:55.960
and brought the Eternals and demons upon us was me.

31:56.990 --> 31:59.280
The one who should have borne the consequences was supposed to be me,

32:01.000 --> 32:02.960
but why was it my father?

32:05.380 --> 32:07.440
What did my father do wrong?

32:10.590 --> 32:13.480
Why was he the one who died in the end?

32:16.270 --> 32:18.790
Why was he the only one who died?

32:19.790 --> 32:21.400
It was all my fault.

32:23.110 --> 32:25.160
I failed to protect Uncle Bai.

32:27.440 --> 32:28.240
Shuo,

32:29.110 --> 32:30.880
go back to the Eternals with me.

32:31.680 --> 32:34.010
Now that the Demon Race is eyeing the Desireless Stone,

32:34.040 --> 32:36.150
only the Eternals can protect you.

32:37.230 --> 32:38.930
That day, in the ruined house outside the city,

32:40.590 --> 32:42.630
you said you'd protect my father.

32:44.070 --> 32:45.720
In Ning'an City,

32:47.690 --> 32:50.340
you also said that with your master and uncle master there,

32:50.280 --> 32:55.240
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

32:52.190 --> 32:54.150
you would definitely keep my father safe.

32:57.830 --> 32:59.590
The Eternals,

32:58.400 --> 33:04.260
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

33:01.310 --> 33:02.400
the demons,

33:04.100 --> 33:04.960
and the humans in this world—

33:06.660 --> 33:09.070
I just realized that I never truly understood them.

33:06.720 --> 33:14.120
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

33:10.540 --> 33:13.540
I thought Eternals could always save humans,

33:15.040 --> 33:20.230
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

33:16.110 --> 33:19.200
but it turned out that it was my wishful thinking.

33:22.030 --> 33:23.920
I was wrong.

33:27.030 --> 33:28.270
Logically,

33:28.710 --> 33:30.170
I have no right to blame you.

33:30.920 --> 33:32.090
But emotionally,

33:33.000 --> 33:34.770
I can't help but blame you.

33:36.370 --> 33:37.720
So, Chong Zhao,

33:42.200 --> 33:43.960
from now on,

33:47.220 --> 33:48.260
we have nothing to do

33:51.090 --> 33:52.370
with each other.

33:54.120 --> 33:57.680
♫Across thousands of miles♫

34:01.340 --> 34:02.610
But there's one thing

34:02.660 --> 34:07.370
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

34:03.590 --> 34:05.590
I hope you'll tell me honestly.

34:06.600 --> 34:09.110
Who cast the demonic poison in Ning'an City?

34:10.030 --> 34:11.150
You want revenge?

34:10.080 --> 34:17.360
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

34:11.630 --> 34:13.030
Tell me!

34:15.790 --> 34:17.420
The Demon Race, Cold Spring Palace,

34:18.010 --> 34:19.179
Zhen Yu,

34:18.380 --> 34:23.300
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

34:20.440 --> 34:21.290
and Fu Ling.

34:25.230 --> 34:26.100
Zhen Yu,

34:27.590 --> 34:28.699
and Fu Ling.

34:29.960 --> 34:31.310
Listen to me, Shuo.

34:31.670 --> 34:33.159
Don't be impulsive.

34:33.510 --> 34:34.880
Zhen Yu is one of the three great Demon Kings.

34:34.900 --> 34:35.610
If you provoke him,

34:35.639 --> 34:36.560
-he will surely…
-Don't worry.

34:39.139 --> 34:40.889
I will live well.

34:43.230 --> 34:44.960
I'll live to the day when I can take revenge

34:44.960 --> 34:46.550
for my father myself.

34:59.080 --> 35:03.200
♫The flowers flew away♫

35:06.780 --> 35:10.730
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

35:14.710 --> 35:21.610
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

35:14.830 --> 35:17.170
[Memorial Tablet of My Father, Bai Xun]

35:22.480 --> 35:28.350
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

35:24.190 --> 35:28.280
-Governor!
-Governor!

35:33.190 --> 35:34.960
♫May I ask, what do the gods see in the world?♫

35:35.140 --> 35:37.160
♫Sadness from infatuation, anger, and parting♫

35:37.370 --> 35:38.900
♫My love brought tears♫

35:38.320 --> 35:40.150
Governor!

35:39.030 --> 35:40.830
♫Greed for gathering, for holding, and for completeness♫

35:40.150 --> 35:41.960
Beat him!

35:41.380 --> 35:43.190
♫I was never a flower, but I withered on my own♫

35:43.580 --> 35:44.830
♫I fell between your brows and became a good fruit♫

35:43.800 --> 35:45.110
Kill him!

35:44.960 --> 35:46.710
♫The grand dream of life is hard to let go♫

35:47.090 --> 35:48.980
♫Searching for the path, the answers, yet found nothing♫

35:49.370 --> 35:50.850
♫With a heart full of compassion for the people, I let go of my obsessions♫

35:51.120 --> 35:52.980
♫I cultivated myself to be free of desires, offering myself as a sacrifice to the moon♫

35:53.480 --> 35:55.170
♫The daylight burns through, and the stars shine bright♫

35:55.390 --> 35:56.950
♫Through the Buddhist dust, I see the moon in the sky♫

35:57.450 --> 35:59.190
♫I am but a mortal, destined to fade♫

35:59.490 --> 36:01.530
♫But I went through a thousand calamities for a promise♫

36:01.760 --> 36:03.450
♫I severed emotions, desires, and the fate between you and me♫

36:03.750 --> 36:05.810
♫To protect the world for eternity♫

36:16.920 --> 36:19.150
Governor, farewell.

36:20.510 --> 36:22.550
They forced Bai Xun to his death.

36:22.570 --> 36:23.780
How dare they come and see him off?

36:24.030 --> 36:26.360
Humans are so hypocritical.

36:26.360 --> 36:28.070
Jin Yao used magic that day.

36:28.510 --> 36:29.800
These humans have already forgotten about

36:29.800 --> 36:31.480
the Eternals, demons, and the Nether Poison.

36:32.150 --> 36:33.400
In their memories,

36:33.400 --> 36:35.310
Bai Xun simply died of an illness in his prime,

36:35.330 --> 36:37.390
with no connection to them.

36:37.410 --> 36:38.930
These Eternals

36:39.000 --> 36:40.580
sure are good at whitewashing.

36:41.330 --> 36:42.260
Master,

36:42.550 --> 36:44.440
when will we bring Bai Shuo back to the Demon Race?

37:08.660 --> 37:11.300
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

37:10.320 --> 37:11.510
Father,

37:12.480 --> 37:13.690
I'm leaving.

37:15.140 --> 37:17.740
The Eternal Race erased the memories of everyone in the city.

37:18.410 --> 37:20.370
They don't know what they've done,

37:22.950 --> 37:24.440
yet they're mourning you,

37:25.820 --> 37:27.220
seeing you off,

37:27.910 --> 37:30.690
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

37:28.400 --> 37:29.880
and weeping for you.

37:31.210 --> 37:32.770
You guarded a city

37:33.510 --> 37:35.120
for your whole life,

37:37.290 --> 37:38.960
and even gave up your life.

37:41.740 --> 37:42.740
Was it worth it?

37:44.390 --> 37:46.550
Chong Zhao asked me to go back to the Eternals with him.

37:47.250 --> 37:48.740
If it were in the past,

37:50.050 --> 37:51.890
I would be so happy.

37:54.800 --> 37:56.510
But now I understand.

37:58.050 --> 37:59.500
The Demon Race is heartless,

38:00.850 --> 38:02.210
the Eternal Race is detached,

38:03.440 --> 38:04.740
and the Human Race is powerless.

38:08.100 --> 38:09.790
No one can be relied on,

38:11.490 --> 38:13.130
and no one can be trusted.

38:15.920 --> 38:17.000
Relying on myself

38:17.690 --> 38:18.920
is better than relying on others.

38:26.840 --> 38:27.950
Don't worry.

38:29.650 --> 38:30.810
One day,

38:31.460 --> 38:33.110
I will be stronger than the Eternals and demons

38:33.950 --> 38:35.750
and I will go to the Cold Spring Palace to avenge you.

38:35.530 --> 38:38.170
[Tomb of My Father, Bai Xun]

38:50.440 --> 38:52.170
If you want to get revenge on the Cold Spring Palace,

38:53.010 --> 38:54.250
you don't need to go through all this trouble.

38:54.400 --> 38:56.340
Who allowed you to come to my father's grave?

38:57.580 --> 38:59.540
Don't you want to get revenge on the Cold Spring Palace?

39:00.320 --> 39:01.030
Join my Polar Realm,

39:01.030 --> 39:02.150
and I'll help you.

39:04.380 --> 39:05.910
The Cold Spring Palace deserves to die.

39:05.930 --> 39:07.240
But what makes you any better?

39:07.510 --> 39:08.840
Did you really have no intention of using me

39:08.840 --> 39:10.150
when you gave me the Ghost Grass?

39:10.150 --> 39:11.480
I remember you saying

39:11.480 --> 39:12.590
it was an equal exchange,

39:12.610 --> 39:13.550
and that gain or loss didn't matter.

39:13.550 --> 39:15.510
The condition for an equal exchange was that my father was alive!

39:15.880 --> 39:20.340
♫No matter if I'm drunk or not, I just want to be reckless once♫

39:22.340 --> 39:23.980
I don't expect a demon to be good,

39:22.410 --> 39:27.810
♫Because love is thrilling♫

39:25.070 --> 39:27.510
but I will never allow you to disturb my father's peace.

39:28.200 --> 39:29.400
Get lost!

39:28.380 --> 39:31.880
♫If you tear open my heart♫

39:32.680 --> 39:34.990
♫I can hold you a little tighter♫

39:35.540 --> 39:40.380
♫This pain will gradually cool♫

39:39.740 --> 39:41.780
I do plan to leave this city.

39:42.510 --> 39:43.280
However,

39:42.600 --> 39:46.330
♫Time withers the moonlight♫

39:44.860 --> 39:46.210
you must go with me.

39:46.880 --> 39:48.360
Why should I go with you?

39:46.960 --> 39:49.250
♫All that's left is pitch darkness♫

39:49.080 --> 39:50.730
You don't have the right to choose.

39:49.700 --> 39:51.310
♫I want to tear apart♫

39:52.340 --> 39:55.130
♫This sky for you♫

39:54.770 --> 39:56.120
Who says I don't?

40:01.410 --> 40:03.900
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

40:04.510 --> 40:07.730
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

40:08.220 --> 40:11.470
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

40:11.900 --> 40:14.370
♫This moment feels like forever♫

40:14.610 --> 40:17.660
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

40:15.690 --> 40:16.690
I told you

40:17.740 --> 40:19.530
not to be disrespectful in front of my father's grave

40:17.800 --> 40:21.660
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

40:20.030 --> 40:21.280
and disturb his peace.

40:21.960 --> 40:23.030
Fan Yue,

40:22.080 --> 40:23.920
♫Even if I'll perish♫

40:23.480 --> 40:25.440
I am just a human.

40:24.120 --> 40:26.890
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

40:25.440 --> 40:27.320
In your eyes, I'm as insignificant as an ant.

40:27.120 --> 40:30.100
♫Burn out my waning moon♫

40:28.070 --> 40:29.800
But even ants will bite

40:29.800 --> 40:31.510
when cornered.

40:30.560 --> 40:35.460
♫Exchanging a lifetime of passion♫

40:36.760 --> 40:38.280
If it weren't for your stirring things up

40:38.280 --> 40:39.440
and watching from the sidelines,

40:39.440 --> 40:40.960
my father wouldn't be lying here!

40:41.470 --> 40:42.760
Fan Yue, remember,

40:43.280 --> 40:45.250
I, Bai Shuo, never let my grudges go,

40:45.960 --> 40:47.230
nor let my anger fade on its own.

40:50.600 --> 40:52.490
You never let your grudges go,

40:52.950 --> 40:54.880
and never let your anger fade on its own?

40:56.430 --> 40:58.660
Are you really not afraid of death just to vent your anger?

40:59.110 --> 41:00.110
I am.

41:01.370 --> 41:03.630
But I'm more afraid that my father can't rest in peace.

41:03.750 --> 41:05.950
A heartless demon like you

41:06.510 --> 41:08.610
would never understand what family means,

41:09.010 --> 41:11.700
nor would you understand my father's loyalty.

41:16.020 --> 41:19.670
Father! Father!

41:19.700 --> 41:21.500
Father!

41:29.220 --> 41:30.180
Let her go!

41:35.580 --> 41:36.870
Without strength,

41:36.920 --> 41:39.060
drawing your sword would only be self-humiliation.

41:39.090 --> 41:40.260
Fan Yue,

41:40.280 --> 41:41.840
if you forcefully take her away,

41:41.870 --> 41:43.630
you'll be the enemy of the entire Lanling Sect.

41:43.630 --> 41:45.360
Fine by me.

41:45.090 --> 41:48.200
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

41:45.710 --> 41:46.790
Go back and tell Jin Yao

41:46.810 --> 41:48.120
I've taken her away.

41:48.150 --> 41:49.070
If he wants to start a war,

41:48.550 --> 41:51.420
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

41:49.090 --> 41:50.410
I'll be waiting in the Polar Realm.

41:52.100 --> 41:55.410
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

41:55.780 --> 41:58.080
♫This moment feels like forever♫

41:58.800 --> 42:01.670
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

42:01.930 --> 42:05.410
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

42:05.870 --> 42:07.830
♫Even if I'll perish♫

42:08.120 --> 42:10.550
♫At least I can still kiss your face♫

42:16.710 --> 42:17.670
Young Lord!

42:24.670 --> 42:26.110
Young Lord!

42:26.110 --> 42:27.030
How are you?

42:27.030 --> 42:28.180
I won't die.

42:28.480 --> 42:31.130
Master hasn't punished you so harshly in a long time.

42:31.160 --> 42:31.910
Young Lord,

42:31.930 --> 42:33.220
I don't understand.

42:33.250 --> 42:35.370
That Chong Zhao only saved you once.

42:35.390 --> 42:37.090
Why are you helping him so much?

42:37.110 --> 42:38.280
Haven't you already

42:38.310 --> 42:39.870
repaid his kindness?

42:39.900 --> 42:40.840
That's not kindness.

42:41.590 --> 42:42.820
Then what is it?

43:01.670 --> 43:03.620
It's a feeling,

43:03.640 --> 43:04.870
a feeling

43:05.140 --> 43:06.830
that I can't even explain.

43:09.500 --> 43:10.790
You don't need to worry about this.

43:10.810 --> 43:12.000
Investigate something for me.

43:12.920 --> 43:13.760
What is it?

43:13.780 --> 43:16.610
Everything about Chong Zhao from his birth until now,

43:16.640 --> 43:17.800
no matter how big or small.

43:18.170 --> 43:20.250
Why do you want to investigate this?

43:20.270 --> 43:22.410
I want him to come into my world,

43:23.860 --> 43:26.040
the world of hell.

43:31.660 --> 43:34.620
[Bright Moon Palace, Demon Race]

43:41.810 --> 43:42.620
Where am I?

43:42.950 --> 43:43.880
The Bright Moon Palace.

43:45.850 --> 43:46.870
I didn't say I'd come here.

43:47.140 --> 43:48.620
Don't you want revenge?

43:49.640 --> 43:51.280
Do you really think Lanling Sect can help you?

43:51.300 --> 43:52.970
That doesn't mean

43:53.000 --> 43:55.330
I have to rely on you.

43:56.250 --> 43:58.040
Even if I don't join the Eternals,

43:58.070 --> 43:59.990
I will never submit to the Demon Race.

44:00.450 --> 44:01.490
I'll choose

44:01.870 --> 44:02.980
my path myself.

44:03.200 --> 44:05.600
No one has the right to decide for me.

44:05.620 --> 44:07.050
So, are you going back

44:07.080 --> 44:09.290
to Ning'an City to step right into the trap,

44:09.570 --> 44:11.450
or are you going to live a wandering, fugitive life?

44:12.510 --> 44:13.480
It has nothing to do with you.

44:13.890 --> 44:16.250
I don't want to get involved in your life or death.

44:16.920 --> 44:18.080
In my eyes,

44:18.610 --> 44:20.560
you're just a vessel for the Desireless Stone.

44:21.080 --> 44:22.910
But the Wunian Stone is mine,

44:23.040 --> 44:24.840
so you are mine too.
